name: pat junior - Golds In (ft. Tyler Donavan)

metadata.description:
I remember putting together this instrumental and putting the words together for this song…

I had been doing some healing and wanted to reflect on this new place in my life within my writing. My music has always been a raw and pure reflection of where I currently am and since I had been doing a lot of growing in such a short time, I needed to invite people into this new space of healing I currently resided in. 

A place of where one can relate, a place of encouragement, a place of peace, place to unite in healing and more.

This also needed to be an introduction to a new pat junior that would be smiling MORE. 

All of those things in my mind and my heart carefully considered, I wrote “Golds In” featuring my homie Tyler Donavan. 

[ join the collectors guild once you collect 

https://guild.xyz/gold-fang-society-comms ]

co-produced by Alex Thompson
